      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">0.99</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·小雅·鹿鳴之什·007.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">采薇.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>昔我往矣，楊柳依依。今我來思，雨雪霏霏。
行道遲遲，載渴載飢。我心傷悲，莫知我哀！</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>At first, when we set out,
The willows were fresh and green;
Now, when we shall be returning,
The snow will be falling in clouds.
Long and tedious will be our marching;
We shall hunger; we shall thirst.
Our hearts are wounded with grief,
And no one knows our sadness.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
